summary: This saved game is a beautiful women that just has got lydia as follower
descriptionHtml:
This game has just got lydia so its a easy start for peole that don`t want to start from the beginning.

Her name is Kate and she is very beautiful.
She also have breezehome in whiterun and around 5000 gold.

How to install:
Unzip the folder And drag Kate.ess file into your saved game folder
Savde game folder can be found under C:\\Users\\(your name)\\Documents\\my games\\skyrim\\saves
The file can now be load when you open the game like a normal save.
You can now play !

To unzip use winzar : http://www.rarlab.com/
